divs: Sighting Detailsi was smoking outside, went to the street looked up, after hoping to see a shooting star, i looked and found two objects moving in two different angles. They began to speed up and then slow down both at their own speeds. They were visuable for around a minute and 9 seconds.After realizing what just happened my vision was very dark like my eyes were dilated and i got chills and sweats.
